"CREATE INDEX [インデックス名] ON [テーブル名] USING GIST ( [ジオメトリカラム"
"名] );"

#. Tag: para
#: using_postgis_dataman.xml:1587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The above syntax will always build a 2D-index. To get the an n-dimensional "
